data.description:
This is a Warm Cozy Family Home!! 
This home has been lived in and loved in.
It was large enough for our Family Farm..
We are expanding and need to move to a larger space!
Our neighbors are great!!  

Recently refreshed - Exterior Stucco Painted!
Yards are a work in progress as they were a part of our farm.
Biola is a quaint small family city. 
Small grocery market around the corner. 

House is being sold in "As Is Condition"
Lot next door is also available for sale by another owner. 
We were told by the owner it is zoned commercial.
